","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"activated through them. Items can be grouped in sections, and may"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"have submenus associated with them. Both items and sections usually"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"have some representation data, such as labels or icons. The type of","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the associated action (ie whether it is stateful, and what kind of"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"state it has) can influence the representation of the item.","type":"text"}],"url":"\/documentation\/gio\/menumodelref","type":"topic","title":"MenuModelRef","kind":"symbol","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"struct","kind":"keyword"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"text":"MenuModelRef","kind":"identifier"}],"navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MenuModelRef"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/GIO\/documentation\/GIO\/MenuModelRef"}}}